Frederick.Oakdale High School (Maryland):
Oakdale High School is an American public high school located in Frederick County, Maryland, in Ijamsville, near the city of Frederick.


== History ==

The school's building was built in 2008 to temporarily hold Linganore High School while Linganore's original building was being renovated. In 2010, the school opened as Oakdale High School with only ninth and tenth grade.
